I apologise for this in advance.

---

**Casa Del Void &ndash; A Star Guardian Holiday**

{{champion:222}} &ldquo;Hey! Hey! Gang! Look! LOOK! I found a travel coupon for the Void! Let&rsquo;s go on a vacation to the Void! I hear its great weather for blowing stuff up this time of the year!&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Ew... nothing but gross things come out of the Void. Why would I want to go there?&rdquo;

{{champion:99}} &ldquo;Ya. Gross things.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Oh-ma-gawd, do you think Poppy came from there?&rdquo;

{{champion:99}} &ldquo;Ya. Totally.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Ew.&rdquo;

{{champion:78}}  (From distant room) &ldquo;I heard that! Don&rsquo;t make me come over there!&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Or else what? You&rsquo;ll tip your protein shake on m-?&rdquo;

**Sploosh**

{{champion:78}} &ldquo;Yerp.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;ARGHHHHH! POPPY YOU BITC-!&rdquo;

{{champion:40}}  &ldquo;Ahri! Watch your mouth, there&rsquo;s a child in the room!&rdquo;

**Points at {{champion:117}}**

{{champion:117}} &ldquo;Heyyyyyyyy! I&rsquo;m older than all of you dewdrops!&rdquo;

{{champion:21}} &ldquo;I heard the locals are a little... weird. Are you sure about this Jinx? Where did you even get this coupon?&rdquo;

{{champion:222}} &ldquo;It was in a Star Guardian Weekly magazine at {{champion:164}}&#039;s Cut and Curl hairdressing salon.&rdquo;

{{champion:16}} &ldquo;I&rsquo;m so happy she decided to follow her passion.&rdquo;

{{champion:40}} &ldquo;I didn&rsquo;t know you started going to the hairdresser...&rdquo;

{{champion:222}} &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t! But that&rsquo;s not the point! The coupon says buy 1 ticket, the next 9 are free!&rdquo;

{{champion:134}} &ldquo;Sounds... desperate.&rdquo;

** {{champion:81}} walks in **

{{champion:81}} &ldquo;Heyyyyy ladiesssss! How ya&rsquo;ll doin? Eh?&rdquo;

{{champion:21}} &ldquo;Ahhh great it&rsquo;s him again. I thought I locked the front door this time.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;EZREAL. YOU&rsquo;RE NOT A STAR GUARDIAN. YOU CAN&rsquo;T JUST PUT ON A SPARKLY OUTFIT AND PRETEND TO BE ONE.&rdquo;

{{champion:134}} &ldquo;Mildly... creepy.&rdquo;

{{champion:99}} &ldquo;Ya. Creepy.&rdquo;

{{champion:40}}  &ldquo;Ezreal, weren&rsquo;t you and {{champion:6}} friends at some point? Why don&rsquo;t you go hang around with him? He was totally into the Star Guardian dress up thing with you. What happened?&rdquo;

{{champion:81}} &ldquo;He got reworked... We don&rsquo;t talk anymore.&rdquo;

{{champion:40}}  &ldquo;Hmmmm.&rdquo;

{{champion:16}} &ldquo;Aw, that&rsquo;s sad.&rdquo;

{{champion:222}} &ldquo;Ouch.&rdquo;

{{champion:81}} &ldquo;... Annyywwaayy. I overheard you wanted to travel to the Void. My friend is a tour guide for the Void... Want me to hook you up... in exchange for membership into the Start Guardians?!&rdquo;

** Silence **

{{champion:117}} &ldquo;Ha... ha-ha... Ha! HA! HA-HA-HA! HA-HA-HA-HAAAAA!&rdquo;

{{champion:40}}  &ldquo;Lulu, hush!&rdquo;

** Silence **

** {{champion:103}} clears throat **

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Fine. FINE! Jinx... buy the ticket. This tour guide better not be some trash tier bronzie Ezreal.&rdquo;

{{champion:81}} &ldquo;He&rsquo;s not. I promise. He&rsquo;s very professional.&rdquo;

** --- Void Tour Inc. Building --- **

{{champion:161}} &ldquo;10 attendees... reflective attire... IQ levels ranging from 60 to 170... gender... all female in appearance...&rdquo;

{{champion:81}} &ldquo;Hey!&rdquo;

{{champion:161}} &ldquo;Hmmmmm. Yes... This trip will most certainly be a terrible one. Here, put these suits on. The Void is unsuitable for... your species.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;If you&rsquo;re going have three tentacles, at least lift.&rdquo;

{{champion:78}} &ldquo;We&rsquo;re stronger than we look you oversized calamari.&rdquo;

** {{champion:161}} looks at {{champion:81}} with a tired expression **

** {{champion:81}}  shrugs **

** --- Stepping Out Of The Rift Into The Void --- **

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;Where&rsquo;s the Star-Guardian-Bucks? I need my bi-daily pumpkin spiced latte.&rdquo;

{{champion:161}} &ldquo;We do not offer such a beverage here. We have Void slime &lsquo;in a glass&rsquo;. Nutritious... but lacking in taste or emotional fulfilment.&rdquo;

{{champion:103}} &ldquo;WHAT?! NO. NO! I NEED MY PUMPKIN SPICED LATTE!&rdquo;

** {{champion:121}}  pops out from behind a Void bush **

{{champion:121}}  H̯̼̗̬̬̞̯E͉̫Ỵ̭̜͠Y̷̜̫Y̷̩Y̻͖̼̖͟ͅK̖̟̭̖̜͎͓͠i̲d͔̻̬Ṣ̬̹W͕̫̲a̶̪͇͈̰̺͍N̵Ņ̩̗̟̲̺ͅa͔̫̱̘̦͙͕B̨͚̫͙̥̲̫u͏̙̘Y͝S͚̞̤̥͠o̻͇m̲̭̠̗Ẹ̼̝̼̬̜V͙͓͓̗̕ó̰͙̺ị̻̰̝̙̺͎͝d̥͈͖̖̦́S͏̯̗͕̥̺̭̺aLT̞̹͖̞̲͈s͉̘̮̦̖̟?!

{{champion:103}}  &ldquo;EW!&rdquo;

** KICK **

**{{champion:121}} goes flying over a nearby wall **

{{champion:161}} &ldquo;Please stay close. I cannot lose any more tour attendees this month or I will be placed on performance review. *Grumble*&rdquo;
